<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer17113102535818240906">I was the first to write about thorium in the mainstream press. My feature story in Wired catalyzed the thorium power movement. I am an award-winning journalist, and my work has appeared in Time, Fortune, The Atlantic, and The Best Science Writing. I am also the editorial director of Pike Research, a leading clean-energy firm. I live in Boulder, Colorado with my wife and son.<br/></span>

